      >
        Two new ActivityPods providers
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        MyPod.store (provided by Virtual Assembly) and Bocage.me (Normandy area)
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ml-10">
      <span
        class="flex absolute -left-5 justify-center items-center w-10 h-10 bg-violet-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900"
      >
        <Icon
          name="ic:baseline-check"
          class="w-6 h-6 text-white dark:text-slate-200"
        />
      </span>
      <time
        class="block mb-2 text-md font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
        >January 2023</time
      >
      <h3
        class="flex items-center mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
      >
        Frontend for ActivityPods providers
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Account and contacts management are split in a separate frontend
        deployed by each Pod provider
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ml-10">
      <span
        class="flex absolute -left-5 justify-center items-center w-10 h-10 bg-violet-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900"
      >
        <Icon
          name="ic:baseline-check"
          class="w-6 h-6 text-white dark:text-slate-200"
        />
      </span>
      <time
        class="block mb-2 text-md font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
        >March 2023</time
      >
      <h3
        class="flex items-center mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
      >
        Public data
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Ability to make data public and to aggregate them in external public
        instances.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ml-10">
      <span
        class="flex absolute -left-5 justify-center items-center w-10 h-10 bg-violet-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900"
      >
        <Icon
          name="ic:baseline-check"
          class="w-6 h-6 text-white dark:text-slate-200"
        />
      </span>
      <time
        class="block mb-2 text-md font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
        >January 2024</time
      >
      <h3
        class="flex items-center mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
      >
        Improved contacts management
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Geolocalization of profiles, contacts grouping, improved invitation by
        email...
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ml-10">
      <span
        class="flex absolute -left-5 justify-center items-center w-10 h-10 bg-violet-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900"
