        class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-sm font-medium mr-2 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded dark:bg-blue-900 dark:text-white ml-3"
        >Work in progress</span
      >
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Allow users to create CODs and manage them collectively
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ml-10">
      <span
        class="flex absolute -left-5 justify-center items-center w-10 h-10 bg-gray-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900"
