        class="flex items-center mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
      >
        Full Solid-OIDC compliance
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Solid clients can connect to ActivityPods Pods just like other Pod providers
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="mb-10 ml-10">
      <span
        class="flex absolute -left-5 justify-center items-center w-10 h-10 bg-gray-500 rounded-full ring-8 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900"
      >
        <Icon
          name="ic:baseline-access-time"
          class="w-6 h-6 text-white dark:text-slate-200"
        />
      </span>
      <time
        class="block mb-2 text-md font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
        >Autumn 2025</time
      >
      <h3
        class="flex items-center mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
      >
        NextGraph integration
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Store Pod data in <a href="https://nextgraph.org/" target="_blank" class="underline">NextGraph</a> so that it may be encrypted and accessed via the NextGraph protocol
      </p>
